msg: Know anyone researching social media (Facebook, Twitter, etc.) and the impact on elections or democracy as a whole? I am specifically interested in research comparing the impact across multiple Asian countries.
I host a new Social Media and Democracy Research Facebook Group connecting researchers WITH practitioners using these tools in politics, media, and government.
